{"id":187425,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/翻墙-linux下用ssh隧道和firefox翻墙/","date":"2011-10-10T12:00:42Z","modified":"2011-10-10T12:00:42Z","title":"翻墙 | Linux下用ssh隧道和Firefox翻墙","content":"<p><p>来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://blog.claudxiao.net/2011/10/how_to_fuck_the_gfw/\">http://blog.claudxiao.net/2011/10/how_to_fuck_the_gfw/</a>  </p>\n<div>\n<p>1. 开启ssh隧道转发：</p>\n<pre>ssh -qTfnN -D 8080 username@your.remote.ssh.server</pre>\n<p>2. 配置Firefox本地代理：Firefox->首选项->高级->网络->连接/设置，选择&#8221;手动配置代理&#8221;，SOCKS主机127.0.0.1，端口8080，类型SOCKSv5。</p>\n<p>3. 开启Firefox的用隧道解析DNS开关：在地址栏输入about:config，在过滤器输入network.proxy.socks_remote_dns，双击该配置项，使其值为true。</p>\n<p>完成。</p>\n<p>PS: Chrome也可以设置代理（首选项->高级选项->更改代理服务器设置），但不能设置DNS，可能导致部分网站的DNS解析失败，比如twitter。</p>\n<p>Reference:</p>\n<p>[1] wormser. HowTo: SSH Tunnel Firefox. <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=723025\">http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=723025</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/xijie.wordpress.com/5164/\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/xijie